<h1>Alfred Megally</h1>

<h2><a href="/">/now</a>: <a href="http://alfredmegally.com/now/">alfredmegally.com/now</a></h2>

<h2>Location:</h2>
<p>
Medellin

Colombia
</p>

<h2>Professional title:</h2>
<p>
Entrepreneur/Ecommerce Consultant/Creative
</p>

<h2>What do you do?</h2>
<p>
I build software and physical products from scratch while connecting with local community in key international cities.
</p>

<h2>Why?</h2>
<p>
I value independence and long stretches of deep thinking. I love making things, learning & teaching, and connecting with diverse creative people from around the world.
</p>

<h2>Recent thought or epiphany?</h2>
<p>
"Help yourself.  Let others help you.  Find opportunities to help others" - Carlos - Eco-reserve founder in the colombian jungle.
</p>

<h2>What should we read?</h2>
